message.entry: Particle filter is not initialized. Initialize the particle filter to use the object.
Occupancy grid map is not assigned. Assign an occupancy grid map to use the object.
Sensor model is not assigned. Assign a valid sensor model to use the object.
모션 모델이 할당되지 않았습니다. 객체를 사용하려면 유효한 모션 모델을 할당하십시오.
Unable to get statistics from one of the clusters.
Cannot compute state estimate. None of the clusters have positive weight.
There are no obstacle free cells in the map. Assigned map must have obstacle free space.
Not enough memory. Reduce the maximum number of particles in ParticleLimits.
Not enough memory. Reduce the size of the occupancy grid in SensorModel.
